==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Slopwork
<hw>Slop"work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The manufacture of
slops, or cheap ready-made clothing; also, such clothing; hence, hasty,
slovenly work of any kind.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>No <qex>slopwork</qex> ever dropped from his [Carlyle's] pen.</q>
<rj><qau>Froude.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slopy</ent>⟦br⟧
